@Node TNG1 "STCCG.guide/Episodes/TNG/Encounter at Farpoint"

  @{b}Encounter at Farpoint@{ub}

The new USS Enterprise, en route to pich up its final crew members and
investigate a mysterious space station, is confronted by a goodlike entity
known as Q who puts Picard, Counselor Troi, Data and security chief Yar on
trial for the crimes of all humanity in the past, a challenge Picard
grudgingly agress to meet.
The crew must solve the mystery of Farpoint station observed by Q.


