@Node TNG3 "STCCG.guide/Episodes/TNG/The Naked Now"

  @{b}The Naked Now@{ub}

An Away Team, after visiting a ship whose crew apparently commited mass
suicide, unwittingly brings a virus aboard the Enterprise - infecting the
crew with a madness that puts the thought of their duties well out of mind -
while a nearby star collapses, hurling a chunk of stellar material straight
toward the Enterprise.


