@Node TNG6 "STCCG.guide/Episodes/TNG/Where No One Has Gone Before"

  @{b}Where No One Has Gone Before@{ub}

A warp drive adjustement - supervised by Starfleet propulsion expert
Kosinski but actually implemented by a beeing called the Traveller -
takes the Enterprise to a dimension where thought becomes reality.
Realizing the dangers, the Traveller expends his remaining reserves
of energy to return the ship to Federation space before fading into
another plane of existance.


