@Node TNG9 "STCCG.guide/Episodes/TNG/The Battle"

  @{b}The Battle@{ub}

The normally greed-driven DaiMon Bok of the Ferengi suddenly becomes bene-
ficent and returns a salvaged piece of Starfleet equipment - Picard's last
command, the U.S.S. Stargazer. Unknown to the crew of the Enterprise, the
ship is part of a plan by Bok to seek revenge on Picard for the death of
his son in the Battle of Maxia.


