@Endnode

@Node TNG16 "STCCG.guide/Episodes/TNG/Too Short A Season"

  @{b}Too Short A Season@{ub}

Facing the potential of repeating a mistake made forty years ago when he
traded arms for hostages and thereby plunged Mordan IV into civil war,
Admiral Mark Jameson gives himself a massive dose of a de-aging drug to
restore his youth prior to beginning hostage negotiations yet again on the
war-torn planet.


