@Node TNG17 "STCCG.guide/Episodes/TNG/When The Bough  Breaks"

  @{b}When The Bough  Breaks@{ub}

After the once-believed-mythical planet of Aldea decloacksin front of the
Enterprise, it's leaders ask for the unthinkable. No longer able to pro-
create - due to the depletion of the ozon layer of their planet by their
pervasive technology - the Aldeans offer to purchase children in exchange
for their advanced scientific knowledge.


