@Node TNG79 "STCCG.guide/Episodes/TNG/Remember Me"

  @{b}Remember Me@{ub}

Dr. Crusher's old friend, Dr. Dalen Quaice, is leaving his former home on
a Starbase to retire after the recent death of his wife. He mentions his
slowly deteroiating memory, a thought which remains on Dr. Chrusher's mind
