investigation is underway, pays a visit to his old friend Boothby, the
Academy gardener since Picard's days as a cadet. Wise old Boothby, and later
Picard himself, begin to wonder if perhaps the surviving cadets of Nova
Squadron aren't simply diverting the responsibility for their own mistake.


