officers aboard the Enterprise. Sito, a Bajoran ensign who was involved in
the Nova sqadron accident cover-up at Starfleet Academy with Wesley Crusher,
is neck-in-neck for a promotion to Ops with the ambitious Lavelle, who is
attempting to make a favorable impression on Commander Riker. Vulcan Ensign
Taurik is an engineering specialist whose duties of late have grown mysterious,
as have those of Nurse Ogawa, who is also due for a promotion. The Enterprise
is undertaking a top secret mission, the true purpose of which is unknown to
the four friends - though each of them has a piece of the puzzle, and a part
