and a woman from his past. Jason turns out to be a rebellious young man
with a record of misdemeanors involving theft and trespassing and a passion
for rock climbing. Bok continues to mysteriously get through the Enterprises's
defenses to threaten Jason's life, until he finally kidnaps Jason and has his
opportunity for vengeance.


