Picard experiences time shifts between three different periods: the present,
a time 25 years in the future and the past, during the Enterprises's first
mission. Q appears to pass the final judgement on humanity. He makes it clear
to Picard that the captain himself is responsible for the disaster of the
entire universe. After Q has shown Picard that the anomaly in the Devron
system grows backwards in time and threatens to prevent the very formation
of life on earth, Picard can find a way to destroy the anomaly using the
ships in the past, present annd future.


